notes.body: Hello Swathi Reddy,     Greetings from PharmEasy!     We refer to your below mail & Order id 6255564     We are trying to contact you on 9866505538 but unfortunately we are unable to connect with you.     We regret to inform you that due to technical issue at pre-analytical stage the Hba1c test got cancelled and we are initiating the B2C  refund Rs 449/- against the Hba1c test  in online source account and amount will be reflected within 3-4 working days.     We understand your concerns & sincerely regret the inconvenience caused to you.     For any further assistance, please reach out to us through our support channels, in the App or website, listed in the 'Need Help' section.   Thank you for choosing PharmEasy. Have a great day ahead!     Regards,  Suraj Gupta  PharmEasy
notes.body_html:
Hello Swathi Reddy,

Greetings from PharmEasy!

We refer to your below mail & Order id 6255564

We are trying to contact you on 9866505538 but unfortunately we are unable to connect with you.

We regret to inform you that due to technical issue at pre-analytical stage the Hba1c test got cancelled and we are initiating the B2C  refund Rs 449/- against the Hba1c test  in online source account and amount will be reflected within 3-4 working days.

We understand your concerns & sincerely regret the inconvenience caused to you.

For any further assistance, please reach out to us through our support channels, in the App or website, listed in the 'Need Help' section. 

Thank you for choosing PharmEasy. Have a great day ahead!

Regards,
Suraj Gupta
PharmEasy

With regards to your order #658015131501068288-19690, as checked due to some unforeseen circumstances, the order was not delivered to you by the expected date of delivery. Please accept my apologies for the same.

Hello Mr.Aggarwal,

Greetings from PharmEasy!
 
This email is with regards to your order #652970963438665728-29988, We apologize for the inconvenience caused to you with your order.

As per update received from our team, please be informed that we have raised a return request for 01 quantity of the TYNOR WALKING STICK TRIPOD SILVER UNIVERSAL SIZE 1 UNIT  on 15th December 2025. Please be informed, items being returned should be in their original manufacturer’s packaging with labels and barcode intact.
 
Please note that the medicine will be collected within 48 hours from the day the request is raised. Once the medicine is returned, it will be verified by our partner retailer at the store. The refund will be processed and initiated within 5 business days. Also, once the refund is initiated it would reflect in your original source account within 7-10 business days.
 
 We appreciate your patience in the meantime.
 
We are marking the ticket as resolved. If you have any queries, please feel free to get back to us.

Thank you for choosing PharmEasy. Have a great day ahead!
